'''Te''' ben wan dringi. Te sey e meki fu ekstrakti fu a teplanta dy e meki sey opo wan teplantasa.

== Infusi ==
A [[Infusi|infusi]] fu te ben:
* Rooibusu: planta ben''Aspalathus linearis''.
* Sonmiksi: abi ondro trawan switiki, sonanisi, fenkelsiri.
* Switiki
* Kamila
* Peprementi
* Fayanetre
* Maté: planta ben ''Ilex paraguariensis''.
* Marihuanate
* Atay Benaanaa/Mentite

== Tongo ==
A wortu te ben ini a [[Sranantongo|Sranantongo]] e kon nanga a [[Bakratongo|Bakratongo]] ''thee'', taki fu [[Sneysikondre|Sneysi]] e kon ina a deytaki fu Fuxian 'tê'. Disi nen ben nanga a Bakraman ini West-[[Ropa|eRopa]] e spredi ([[Franstongo|Franstongo]]: 'thé', [[Ingristongo|Ingris]]: 'tea', [[Doysritongo|Doysritongo]]: 'Tee', [[wp/srn.Italiyanotongo|Italiyanotongo]]: 'tè'). Ini a Mandarinitongo ben te 'cha' leki a [[Rusitongo|Rusitongo]] nanga a [[Portugesotongo|Portugesotongo]].

